Patch: %n.patch
PatchScript: perl -pi -e 's/icewm-\$\(VERSION\)/%n/g' Makefile.in src/Makefile.in
GCC: 4.0
ConfigureParams: --with-docdir=%p/share/doc --mandir=%p/share/man --with-cfgdir=%p/etc/icewm --enable-guievents --enable-menus-gnome2 --with-xpm --with-icesound=esd
Conflicts: icewm, icewm-basic, icewm-gnome2
Replaces: icewm, icewm-basic, icewm-gnome2
InstallScript: <<
 make install install-docs install-man install-gnome DESTDIR=%d 
<<
Description: X11 window manager - with GNOME2 support
DescDetail: <<
 icewm is a nice window manager designed for speed, usability and
 consistency. It is able to emulate the look of Motif, OS/2, Windows
 and allows to have a customizable look using pixmaps.
<<
